                        <interp inst="t18351026-name-724" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>CHARLES GRANT</persName>
                  </hi>. (<hi rend="italic">police-constable H</hi> 25.) I was sent for to Mr. Mes<lb></lb>senger's and the witness, Baxter, brought me this sheet, this leather, and shoes, and other things.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18351026-name-725" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18351026-name-725" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
